snippet.title: Sumotori Dreams Gameplay
snippet.description:
One of the best games ever created.  The game is simple with only a few controls, yet it is infinitely complex.  96k of glory.  Excellent job Archee (the creator of the game).   

Note: I was the loser blue on the right.  I didn't play to win, I played to show off how zanny the game is.  The pelvic thrusts are too much for white at the end.  

You can download the game here: http://www.gravitysensation.com/sumotori/
